uniChess

Class Player<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uniChess.Player<T>

  • public class Player<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    An object representing a Player in a chess game. Each Player has a color and an Identifier of type T. Two players of opposite color are required to initiate a Game.
